ExperiencePCTasksComment:
Some snippets with many variables were difficult due to hard to remember
variable names
ProblemSolvingStrategies:
code snippets with more variables required active effort to remember what
each variable stores, especially if what snippet does was not known.
ChangeComprehension:
Some long code snippets caused slight frustration when they were
presented due to the expectation of many variables
TAComprehensionComment:
On most snippets i did not pay much attention to type annotations, but in
some less clear cases they felt helpful to see what type of data we are
working with
TAComprehensionGeneralComment:
In complex cases and especially with custom types it can help a lot to have
some additional information on what data one is working with.
LaterCodeSnippets:
earlier snippets felt somewhat easier to comprehend as they had generally
shorter identifiers and less length in the snippets
